<title>kl mftwḥ ạlʿynyn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (kl mftwḥ ạlʿynyn .. fy ạlḥq hw lk ʿạbd
 wlys kl mn nṭq .. bạsmk rby qd sẖạhd)2
 (fkl rạʾiⁿ hw ʿạrfuⁿ .. bk wfy qrbk hw sạjd
 wlys kl mn ʿlm .. wqṭʿ msạfẗaⁿ lk wạjd)2
 ạlqrạr- (yạ rb ạ̹ftḥ ly ʿyny .. fạ̉ḥyạ sjdẗaⁿ lạ tnthy
 wbrwḥk qds ʿmqy .. bạlḥb lwqfẗ ạlạ̉bd)2
 2- (fạlqrb lm ạ̉ʿrf mʿnạh .. ạ̹lạ ḥyn ạ̹mtlạ̉t ʿyny
 wfy qrbk ʿrf ạlbʿd .. ạ̉nh ḥrmạny mn ʿyny)2
 (fmạ mn bʿdiⁿ yḥrmny .. mn nwriⁿ tṭlb bh ʿyny
 wmạ mn qrbiⁿ ạ̉hlny .. lnwriⁿ ạ̉kbr mn ʿyny)2</lyrics>
